5
00:00:11,470 --> 00:00:15,380
Kau tahu berapa lama aku menunggu saat ini?

6
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:18,530
Kuharap kau menyukainya.

7
00:00:19,340 --> 00:00:20,860
Ini, Ji Won.

8
